<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .otp { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #2563eb; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p>Hello <%= adminName %>,</p>
        <p>You have requested to change the status of user <strong><%= userName %> (<%= userEmail %>)</strong>.</p>
        <p>Current status: <strong><%= currentStatus %></strong></p>
        <p>Requested status: <strong><%= newStatus %></strong></p>
        <p>Your OTP is: <span class="otp"><%= otp %></span></p>
        <p>This OTP is valid for 10 minutes.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you didn't request this change, please contact support immediately.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>